    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This report is fishy. In your reproduction case, you're building your example code with tsan, but you're not building gRPC itself with tsan. So you're getting tsan reports from code that's not instrumented with tsan to begin with.\r\n\r\nYou can build gRPC with tsan by doing `make CONFIG=tsan`."
