    "body": "I don't know whether this is a valid race condition or not, but it's common to build like this against an unsanitized version of grpc; lots of users aren't going to want build and install a separate version of grpc just for tsan.\r\n\r\nIf it's a false positive, could you add attributes around the functions so that tsan doesn't complain?"
